    <section class="performing-arts-section">
      <div class="container text-center">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Personalize your Performing Arts Lessons with Little Flower’s</h2>
        <p class="lead mb-5">Express yourself with the gift of music! Expand your skills with teachers who prioritize
          your
